** [[Graham Land]]
** [[Palmer Land]]

* [[Ellsworth Land]] with
** [[English Coast]]
** [[Bryan Coast]]
** [[Eights Coast]]

* [[Marie Byrd Land]] with
** [[Walgreen Coast]]
** [[Bakutis Coast]]
** [[Hobbs Coast]]
** [[Ruppert Coast]]
** [[Saunders Coast]]

* [[King Edward VII Land]] with
** [[Shirase Coast]]

