==East Antarctica==
[[File:Antarctica.svg|thumb|400px|East Antarctica on the right.]]
[[East Antarctica]] is the larger part of the continent, both the [[South Magnetic Pole]] and geographic [[South Pole]] are situated here. Divided into:

===Areas===
* [[Coats Land]]

* [[Queen Maud Land]] with
** [[Princess Martha Coast]]
** [[Princess Astrid Coast]]
** [[Princess Ragnhild Coast]]
** [[Prince Harald Coast]]
** [[Prince Olav Coast]]

* [[Enderby Land]]

* [[Kemp Land]]

* [[Mac. Robertson Land]]

* [[Princess Elizabeth Land]]

* [[Wilhelm II Land]]

* [[Queen Mary Land]]

* [[Wilkes Land]]

* [[Adélie Land]]

* [[George V Land]]

* [[Oates Land]]

* [[Victoria Land]]

